    • monthSelected

      public void monthSelected()
      The monthSelected method runs whenever a new selection is made in the month or year combo boxes. It updates the displayed list of types of Appointments and the frequency of those Appointments for that specific month. Lambda Expressions: Lambda expressions were used to loop through each Appointment to get a list of unique types, then loops back through the list of unique types and sorts the Appointments for the current month by type.
